## 🟠 HIGH Findings

### H-01: AI Chat Endpoint Leaks Business Data to Demo Users

| Field | Detail |
|-------|--------|
| **File** | [AiChatController.php](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Http/Controllers/AiChatController.php) + [StoreDataService.php](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Services/StoreDataService.php) |
| **Route** | `POST /ai-chat/ask` |
| **Issue** | `StoreDataService::getContext()` query **semua data bisnis** (revenue, profit, stok, member count, supplier list) **tanpa mempertimbangkan demo global scopes**. Demo user di-scope oleh middleware, tetapi [StoreDataService](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Services/StoreDataService.php#16-220) langsung query model tanpa check |
| **Impact** | Demo user bisa melihat **data keuangan real** (revenue, profit, supplier names) melalui AI chat |

**Evidence:** [StoreDataService](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Services/StoreDataService.php#16-220) query langsung ke [Transaction](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Models/Transaction.php#10-68), `Member`, [Supplier](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Services/StoreDataService.php#198-202), [CashierItem](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Models/CashierItem.php#11-59) — jika demo scopes hanya berlaku per-request via middleware, dan AI chat dikerjakan dalam request yang sama, maka scope harusnya aktif. **TETAPI** — jika ada cached data atau scope tidak tercakup (misal `Supplier::count()`), data real bisa bocor.

**Fix:**
```php
// Di AiChatController::ask(), cek demo user
public function ask(Request $request) {
    if (isDemoUser()) {
        return response()->json([
            'success' => true,
            'reply' => '🔒 Fitur AI Chat tidak tersedia di mode demo.',
        ]);
    }
    // ... existing logic
}
```

